commit a2e5cf536b9ddd7515a3bc5486384eaa7d025417
Author: Mike O'Connell <moc835@gmail.com>
Date:   Sun Jun 7 00:14:17 2026 -0400

    feat: add FullCalendar monthly view to public schedule page (Story 21.2)
    
    Adds a Table/Calendar toggle on desktop (≥992px) that switches between
    the existing DataTables view and a FullCalendar v5.11.3 monthly grid.
    Events are color-coded by category (blue/grey/amber/purple), clickable
    events show a Bootstrap popover with game details, team name search
    filters events client-side, and URL state (?tab=calendar) is preserved
    across filter form submissions and direct links.
    
    Co-Authored-By: Claude Sonnet 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>

